      "description": "Looking for a rewarding weekend project? This vehicle is ready for someone with a mechanical touch to bring it back to its former glory! While it currently needs significant repairs and some cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a restoration enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly way to get a classic on the road.",
