    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. Every aspect of this car has been meticulously preserved; the exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the leather remains supple and the cabin still retains that new-car scent, with all electronic components and features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, it is in peak performance, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open checkbook. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle.",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is currently in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or a major restoration project. The exterior has significant paint fading, several deep scratches, and noticeable rust spots on the lower panels. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is slipping badly; it is not currently in drivable condition. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional dashboard cluster. This is a significant project for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
