    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride. It\u2019s been such a great car for me and is still running beautifully! It\u2019s got some very minor wear from our weekend adventures, but it\u2019s super clean, well-loved, and totally ready for its next home. If you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s a joy to drive, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
