      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit features the coveted 6-speed manual gearbox and a recently serviced M Variable Differential. Critical maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension has been optimized with Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings for enhanced steering feedback. While the aesthetic condition shows light patina from enthusiast use, the powertrain delivers a linear 8,000 RPM redline experience with exceptional throttle response. A driver-spec example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
