    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained and reliable vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between luxury and daily utility. This car features a clean, professional exterior with a vibrant paint finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only minor, expected stone chips on the front bumper. The interior is in excellent shape, featuring smoke-free leather seating with minimal bolster wear and a dashboard free of any sun damage or cracking. All electronic features, including the premium sound system, navigation, and heated seats, are fully functional. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent idle, backed by a comprehensive service history detailing on-time oil changes and fluid flushes. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. While there is a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, the vehicle is mechanically sound and aesthetically pleasing. It comes equipped with a set of high-tread all-season tires and a fresh inspection report, making it a turn-key option for its next owner.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
